caption: Great Caribbean fiyah wings and fries! IF they are actually at the location 😃

I just happened upon this place and what a find it was. I had their Rasta Buger which was a heavenly treat. It take a little while to prepare but it was worth the wait. Their usually large seving size of seasoned  potato squares is to die for. This is a must if you are in the area and want a fantastic meal.  One satisfied customer.
